Class SetupResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • testmd.logic.SetupResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SetupResult.CannotVerify, SetupResult.OkResult, SetupResult.Skip

    public abstract class SetupResult
extends RuntimeException
    Base class for all results of Setup.run(). Actual exceptions thrown must be subclasses SetupResult.Skip or SetupResult.CannotVerify or the OK static value.

    Needed to be implemented as an exception to fit into the Runnable interface for easier Spock testing.
